node.text: @emilybrowns I hope I'm not too late to react but nuuu 😭😭
Farewell @dfsofficial I'm going to miss being able to browse through your alcohol selection as a first "Welcome back" to Singapore and reminisce drinking with @0hso_lovely and friends :(

[MOTHERSHIP GIVEAWAY]

We’re giving away four sets of wines from DFS Wines & Spirits, Changi Airport! Each set comes with two bottles of wine (2014 Chateau Croizet-Bages, Pauillac), worth S$80 in total.

To take part:
1. Follow @mothershipsg and @dfsofficial
2. Tag a friend you would drink the wine with
3. Comment a farewell message for DFS Wines & Spirits, Changi Airport, which will be exiting this June.

This giveaway is only open to Singapore residents above 18. Winners will be required to provide proof of age. #DrinkResponsibly 
Contest ends May 31, 11:59pm. Good luck!
